{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":739,"text":"I have spent the last years"},{"time":2739,"text":"trying to resolve two enigmas:"},{"time":5398,"text":"Why is productivity so disappointing"},{"time":9759,"text":"in all the companies where I work?"},{"time":11641,"text":"I have worked with more than 500 companies."},{"time":15335,"text":"Despite all the technological advances --"},{"time":17780,"text":"computers, I.T., communications, telecommunications,"},{"time":21072,"text":"the Internet."},{"time":23433,"text":"Enigma number two:"},{"time":24831,"text":"Why is there so little engagement at work?"},{"time":27863,"text":"Why do people feel so miserable,"},{"time":29967,"text":"even actively disengaged?"},{"time":33617,"text":"Disengaging their colleagues."},{"time":35141,"text":"Acting against the interest of their company."},{"time":39872,"text":"Despite all the affiliation events,"},{"time":43976,"text":"the celebration, the people initiatives,"},{"time":47973,"text":"the leadership development programs to train"},{"time":50572,"text":"managers on how to better motivate their teams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54956,"text":"At the beginning, I thought there was"},{"time":56694,"text":"a chicken and egg issue:"},{"time":58663,"text":"Because people are less engaged, \nthey are less productive."},{"time":61215,"text":"Or vice versa, because they are less productive,"},{"time":63452,"text":"we put more pressure and they are less engaged."},{"time":65643,"text":"But as we were doing our analysis"},{"time":67511,"text":"we realized that there was a common root cause"},{"time":69432,"text":"to these two issues"},{"time":70815,"text":"that relates, in fact, to the basic \npillars of management."},{"time":75371,"text":"The way we organize is based on two pillars."},{"time":78541,"text":"The hard -- structure, processes, systems."},{"time":81294,"text":"The soft --"},{"time":82518,"text":"feelings, sentiments, interpersonal\nrelationships, traits, personality."},{"time":87973,"text":"And whenever a company"},{"time":89445,"text":"reorganizes, restructures, reengineers,"},{"time":93155,"text":"goes through a cultural transformation program,"},{"time":95603,"text":"it chooses these two pillars."},{"time":97633,"text":"Now, we try to refine them,"},{"time":99682,"text":"we try to combine them."},{"time":101578,"text":"The real issue is --"},{"time":103206,"text":"and this is the answer to the two enigmas --"},{"time":105243,"text":"these pillars are obsolete."},{"time":108177,"text":"Everything you read in business books is based"},{"time":110859,"text":"either on one or the other"},{"time":112524,"text":"or their combination."},{"time":113791,"text":"They are obsolete."},{"time":115105,"text":"How do they work"},{"time":117402,"text":"when you try to use these approaches"},{"time":119689,"text":"in front of the new complexity of business?"},{"time":121837,"text":"The hard approach, basically \nis that you start from strategy,"},{"time":124834,"text":"requirements, structures, processes, \nsystems, KPIs, scorecards,"},{"time":128463,"text":"committees, headquarters, hubs, clusters,"},{"time":131340,"text":"you name it."},{"time":132450,"text":"I forgot all the metrics, incentives, committees, \nmiddle offices and interfaces."},{"time":137881,"text":"What happens basically on the left,"},{"time":139876,"text":"you have more complexity, the \nnew complexity of business."},{"time":143140,"text":"We need quality, cost, reliability, speed."},{"time":147427,"text":"And every time there is a new requirement,"},{"time":149813,"text":"we use the same approach."},{"time":151292,"text":"We create dedicated structure processed systems,"},{"time":154405,"text":"basically to deal with the \nnew complexity of business."},{"time":157643,"text":"The hard approach creates just complicatedness"},{"time":161382,"text":"in the organization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163220,"text":"Let's take an example."},{"time":164798,"text":"An automotive company, the engineering division"},{"time":167694,"text":"is a five-dimensional matrix."},{"time":169486,"text":"If you open any cell of the matrix,"},{"time":171518,"text":"you find another 20-dimensional matrix."},{"time":174531,"text":"You have Mr. Noise, Mr. Petrol Consumption,"},{"time":177394,"text":"Mr. Anti-Collision Properties."},{"time":179352,"text":"For any new requirement,"},{"time":181182,"text":"you have a dedicated function"},{"time":183057,"text":"in charge of aligning engineers against"},{"time":185846,"text":"the new requirement."},{"time":187394,"text":"What happens when the new \nrequirement emerges?"},{"time":189993,"text":"Some years ago, a new requirement"},{"time":192085,"text":"appeared on the marketplace:"},{"time":193932,"text":"the length of the warranty period."},{"time":196083,"text":"So therefore the new requirement is repairability,"},{"time":199018,"text":"making cars easy to repair."},{"time":200518,"text":"Otherwise when you bring the car \nto the garage to fix the light,"},{"time":204524,"text":"if you have to remove the engine"},{"time":206781,"text":"to access the lights,"},{"time":208110,"text":"the car will have to stay one week in the garage"},{"time":210549,"text":"instead of two hours, and the \nwarranty budget will explode."},{"time":213436,"text":"So, what was the solution using the hard approach?"},{"time":216381,"text":"If repairability is the new requirement,"},{"time":219431,"text":"the solution is to create a new function,"},{"time":221520,"text":"Mr. Repairability."},{"time":223693,"text":"And Mr. Repairability creates \nthe repairability process."},{"time":227636,"text":"With a repairability scorecard, \nwith a repairability metric"},{"time":231494,"text":"and eventually repairability incentive."},{"time":234308,"text":"That came on top of 25 other KPIs."},{"time":238072,"text":"What percentage of these people is variable compensation?"},{"time":241578,"text":"Twenty percent at most, divided by 26 KPIs,"},{"time":245405,"text":"repairability makes a difference of 0.8 percent."},{"time":249502,"text":"What difference did it make in their actions,"},{"time":251562,"text":"their choices to simplify? Zero."},{"time":254184,"text":"But what occurs for zero impact? \nMr. Repairability, process,"},{"time":257849,"text":"scorecard, evaluation, coordination \nwith the 25 other coordinators"},{"time":262522,"text":"to have zero impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264418,"text":"Now, in front of the new complexity of business,"},{"time":266959,"text":"the only solution is not drawing boxes"},{"time":269896,"text":"with reporting lines."},{"time":272322,"text":"It is basically the interplay."},{"time":275407,"text":"How the parts work together."},{"time":277978,"text":"The connections, the interactions, the synapses."},{"time":282710,"text":"It is not the skeleton of boxes, \nit is the nervous system"},{"time":287213,"text":"of adaptiveness and intelligence."},{"time":290250,"text":"You know, you could call it cooperation, basically."},{"time":293150,"text":"Whenever people cooperate,"},{"time":295689,"text":"they use less resources. In everything."},{"time":299617,"text":"You know, the repairability issue"},{"time":302149,"text":"is a cooperation problem."},{"time":304901,"text":"When you design cars, please take into account"},{"time":308122,"text":"the needs of those who will repair the cars"},{"time":310830,"text":"in the after sales garages."},{"time":313937,"text":"When we don't cooperate we need more time,"},{"time":316554,"text":"more equipment, more systems, more teams."},{"time":320336,"text":"We need -- When procurement, supply \nchain, manufacturing don't cooperate"},{"time":325427,"text":"we need more stock, more inventories, \nmore working capital."},{"time":328205,"text":"Who will pay for that?"},{"time":330146,"text":"Shareholders? Customers?"},{"time":332108,"text":"No, they will refuse."},{"time":333439,"text":"So who is left? \nThe employees,"},{"time":336248,"text":"who have to compensate through their super"},{"time":338956,"text":"individual efforts for the lack of cooperation."},{"time":342276,"text":"Stress, burnout, they are \noverwhelmed, accidents."},{"time":345944,"text":"No wonder they disengage."},{"time":348768,"text":"How do the hard and the soft\ntry to foster cooperation?"},{"time":352565,"text":"The hard: In banks, when there is a problem"},{"time":357195,"text":"between the back office and the front office,"},{"time":360255,"text":"they don't cooperate. What is the solution?"},{"time":362345,"text":"They create a middle office."},{"time":365440,"text":"What happens one year later?"},{"time":367476,"text":"Instead of one problem \nbetween the back and the front,"},{"time":369484,"text":"now I have two problems."},{"time":370838,"text":"Between the back and the middle"},{"time":371961,"text":"and between the middle and the front."},{"time":374177,"text":"Plus I have to pay for the middle office."},{"time":376642,"text":"The hard approach is unable to foster cooperation."},{"time":379900,"text":"It can only add new boxes, \nnew bones in the skeleton."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384336,"text":"The soft approach:"},{"time":385971,"text":"To make people cooperate, we need \nto make them like each other."},{"time":389800,"text":"Improve interpersonal feelings,"},{"time":391494,"text":"the more people like each other, \nthe more they will cooperate."},{"time":394450,"text":"It is totally wrong."},{"time":396221,"text":"It is even counterproductive."},{"time":398621,"text":"Look, at home I have two TVs. Why?"},{"time":401037,"text":"Precisely not to have to cooperate with my wife."},{"time":403909,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":405549,"text":"Not to have to impose tradeoffs to my wife."},{"time":408453,"text":"And why I try not to impose tradeoffs to my wife"},{"time":412463,"text":"is precisely because I love my wife."},{"time":415130,"text":"If I didn't love my wife, one TV would be enough:"},{"time":418355,"text":"You will watch my favorite football game,"},{"time":420850,"text":"if you are not happy, how is the book or the door?"},{"time":423405,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":424608,"text":"The more we like each other,"},{"time":426489,"text":"the more we avoid the real cooperation"},{"time":429102,"text":"that would strain our relationships \nby imposing tough tradeoffs."},{"time":433276,"text":"And we go for a second TV or we escalate"},{"time":436283,"text":"the decision above for arbitration."},{"time":439207,"text":"Definitely, these approaches are obsolete."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443916,"text":"To deal with complexity, to enhance the nervous system,"},{"time":447699,"text":"we have created what we call \nthe smart simplicity approach"},{"time":450961,"text":"based on simple rules."},{"time":452481,"text":"Simple rule number one:"},{"time":454743,"text":"Understand what others do."},{"time":457768,"text":"What is their real work?"},{"time":459665,"text":"We need to go beyond the boxes,"},{"time":463300,"text":"the job descriptions, beyond the surface"},{"time":467318,"text":"of the container, to understand the real content."},{"time":470823,"text":"Me, designer, if I put a wire here,"},{"time":473531,"text":"I know that it will mean that we will have to"},{"time":475534,"text":"remove the engine to access the lights."},{"time":478100,"text":"Second, you need to reenforce integrators."},{"time":480948,"text":"Integrators are not middle \noffices, they are managers,"},{"time":484808,"text":"existing managers that you reinforce"},{"time":486569,"text":"so that they have power and interest"},{"time":489003,"text":"to make others cooperate."},{"time":491166,"text":"How can you reinforce your \nmanagers as integrators?"},{"time":494898,"text":"By removing layers."},{"time":496373,"text":"When there are too many layers"},{"time":497737,"text":"people are too far from the action,"},{"time":499287,"text":"therefore they need KPIs, metrics,"},{"time":501401,"text":"they need poor proxies for reality."},{"time":505729,"text":"They don't understand reality"},{"time":507331,"text":"and they add the complicatedness of metrics, KPIs."},{"time":510431,"text":"By removing rules -- the bigger we are,"},{"time":512883,"text":"the more we need integrators,"},{"time":514516,"text":"therefore the less rules we must have,"},{"time":516837,"text":"to give discretionary power to managers."},{"time":520731,"text":"And we do the opposite --"},{"time":521858,"text":"the bigger we are, the more rules we create."},{"time":524044,"text":"And we end up with the Encyclopedia \nBritannica of rules."},{"time":527294,"text":"You need to increase the quanitity of power"},{"time":529394,"text":"so that you can empower everybody"},{"time":531122,"text":"to use their judgment, their intelligence."},{"time":534108,"text":"You must give more cards to people"},{"time":536259,"text":"so that they have the critical mass of cards"},{"time":539616,"text":"to take the risk to cooperate,"},{"time":541575,"text":"to move out of insulation."},{"time":543330,"text":"Otherwise, they will withdraw. They will disengage."},{"time":545694,"text":"These rules, they come from game theory"},{"time":547940,"text":"and organizational sociology."},{"time":550168,"text":"You can increase the shadow of the future."},{"time":553020,"text":"Create feedback loops that expose people"},{"time":555921,"text":"to the consequences of their actions."},{"time":558522,"text":"This is what the automotive company did"},{"time":560466,"text":"when they saw that Mr. Repairability had no impact."},{"time":563256,"text":"They said to the design engineers:"},{"time":564891,"text":"Now, in three years, when the new \ncar is launched on the market,"},{"time":569586,"text":"you will move to the after sales \nnetwork, and become in charge"},{"time":572530,"text":"of the warranty budget,"},{"time":574905,"text":"and if the warranty budget explodes,"},{"time":578284,"text":"it will explode in your face. (Laughter)"},{"time":580951,"text":"Much more powerful than 0.8 \npercent variable compensation."},{"time":586892,"text":"You need also to increase reciprocity,"},{"time":590614,"text":"by removing the buffers that make us self-sufficient."},{"time":594329,"text":"When you remove these buffers,"},{"time":596801,"text":"you hold me by the nose, I hold you by the ear."},{"time":599798,"text":"We will cooperate."},{"time":601180,"text":"Remove the second TV."},{"time":602720,"text":"There are many second TVs at work"},{"time":604964,"text":"that don't create value,"},{"time":606265,"text":"they just provide dysfunctional self-sufficiency."},{"time":610953,"text":"You need to reward those who cooperate"},{"time":613382,"text":"and blame those who don't cooperate."},{"time":615061,"text":"The CEO of The Lego Group,"},{"time":618130,"text":"Jorgen Vig Knudstorp, has a great way to use it."},{"time":620953,"text":"He says, blame is not for failure,"},{"time":623858,"text":"it is for failing to help or ask for help."},{"time":628393,"text":"It changes everything."},{"time":630772,"text":"Suddenly it becomes in my\ninterest to be transparent"},{"time":633292,"text":"on my real weaknesses, my real forecast,"},{"time":635332,"text":"because I know I will not be blamed if I fail,"},{"time":637418,"text":"but if I fail to help or ask for help."},{"time":641286,"text":"When you do this, it has a lot of implications"},{"time":644213,"text":"on organizational design."},{"time":647158,"text":"You stop drawing boxes, dotted lines, full lines;"},{"time":649576,"text":"you look at their interplay."},{"time":650966,"text":"It has a lot of implications on financial policies"},{"time":653945,"text":"that we use."},{"time":655159,"text":"On human resource management practices."},{"time":657781,"text":"When you do that, you can manage complexity,"},{"time":660205,"text":"the new complexity of business,"},{"time":661798,"text":"without getting complicated."},{"time":664731,"text":"You create more value with lower cost."},{"time":668381,"text":"You simultaneously improve \nperformance and satisfaction at work"},{"time":672955,"text":"because you have removed the common root cause"},{"time":675684,"text":"that hinders both."},{"time":677300,"text":"Complicatedness: This is your \nbattle, business leaders."},{"time":682010,"text":"The real battle is not against competitors."},{"time":684837,"text":"This is rubbish, very abstract."},{"time":687258,"text":"When do we meet competitors to fight them?"},{"time":689921,"text":"The real battle is against ourselves,"},{"time":692822,"text":"against our bureaucracy, our complicatedness."},{"time":696176,"text":"Only you can fight, can do it."},{"time":699333,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":701420,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}